Title: 'Woman, art and freedom '
DateModified: '2019-03-10'
DatePublished: '2019-03-10'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/woman-art-and-freedom
SetInCountry: Brazil
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Sarah  Santos
AuthorCountry: Brazil
Text: There was a little girl who, since childhood, She was always very adventurous
  and pioneering. However, She had many overproductive parents. However, It was not
  possible to destroy her dreams of one day being a free woman. Then, suddenly, moving
  on the social networks, She finds a possibility to spend time outside, living the
  woman in literature and the world. Look how great! In this experience, She discovered
  something She had never felt in her life. The mystery of being a free woman. In
  this experience She discovered more, It was a moment of much knowledge and deepening
  in what She was. So, when She returned from this trip, the world opened up even
  more, now It is a journey into herself. Becoming more recognized and internationally.
  After that, She began to write her biography. Finally, with great fame stayed and
  today has one of the great female names in Brazilian literature!
